Source code in <code>nemo_retriever/ingestor.py</code> <pre><code>def _merge_params[T](params: T | None, kwargs: dict[str, Any]) -&gt; T:
    if params is None:
        return kwargs  # type: ignore[return-value]
    if not kwargs:
        return params
    if hasattr(params, "model_copy"):
        return params.model_copy(update=kwargs)  # type: ignore[return-value]
    return params
